PN,44701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FToxicologists have told an inquest it
OL,8,Fcannot be ruled out that Noah Donohoe
OL,9,Fmay have had drugs in his system at
OL,10,Fthe time of his death.
OL,12,FForensic analysts said there was no
OL,13,Fevidence that the schoolboy was under
OL,14,Fthe influence of drugs or alcohol, but
OL,15,Fthe presence of some substances
OL,16,Fincluding so-called "designer drugs"
OL,17,Fcannot be excluded because of the
OL,18,Flimits of testing.
OL,26,@xD@UOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,8,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,9,Fin a storm drain tunnel in north
OL,10,FBelfast in June 2020, six days after
OL,11,Fhe left home on his bike to meet two
OL,12,Ffriends in the Cavehill area of
OL,13,FBelfast.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FForensic scientist Amy Eleanor Quinn,
OL,8,Fwho carried out a toxicological
OL,9,Fanalysis on samples from Noah's body
OL,10,Fin July 2020, gave evidence to the
OL,11,Finquest at Belfast Coroners Court on
OL,12,FWednesday, alongside Dr Simon Elliott,
OL,13,Fconsultant forensic toxicologist, who
OL,14,Fcarried out a review and further
OL,15,Ftesting of samples in November 2024.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FIn a joint statement they agreed that
OL,8,FMs Quinn had found evidence of a small
OL,9,Famount of alcohol in Noah's blood but
OL,10,Fthat this was consistent with having
OL,11,Fbeen generated by the body after death
OL,12,Fand there was no reason to believe he
OL,13,Fhad consumed alcohol in the hours
OL,14,Fbefore he died.
OL,16,FThey further agreed "there is no
OL,17,Ftoxicological evidence that the
OL,18,Fdeceased was under the influence of
OL,19,Fdrugs at the time of his death within
OL,20,Fthe range of screening performed".
OL,26,@xD@UOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThey also agreed that "it is not
OL,8,Fpossible to exclude that drugs not
OL,9,Fincluded in the scope of analysis may
OL,10,Fhave been present at the time of his
OL,11,Fdeath".
OL,13,FReiterating there is no toxicological
OL,14,Fevidence that Noah was under the
OL,15,Finfluence of drugs at the time of his
OL,16,Fdeath, they added "this cannot be
OL,17,Fstated with absolute certainty" as
OL,18,F"many drugs exist outside the scope of
OL,19,Ftesting performed in this case and the
OL,20,Finstability of drugs" must be
OL,21,Fconsidered.
OL,26,@oD@WOUsD@FO]xD@SOUyD@_O]zD@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMs Quinn read a statement in which she
OL,8,Fconfirmed she had tested Noah's blood
OL,9,Fsample for a range of drugs including
OL,10,Fmethamphetamine, ecstasy,
OL,11,Fbenzodiazepines, cocaine, cannabis,
OL,12,Fketamine, opiates and fentanyl, as
OL,13,Fwell as pharmaceuticals like
OL,14,Fantidepressants and paracetamol, none
OL,15,Fof which produced a positive result.
OL,17,FShe confirmed that some hallucinogens
OL,18,Flike LSD or magic mushrooms were not
OL,19,Fincluded in these tests.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDr Elliott said in a statement that
OL,8,Fthe "range of screening is such that
OL,9,Fthe testing can only exclude the drugs
OL,10,Fcovered" and "it is not realistically
OL,11,Fpossible to cover the thousands of
OL,12,Fdrugs/substances that could be
OL,13,Finvolved".
OL,15,FHe also added that the "limit of
OL,16,Fdetection is fundamental" and that
OL,17,Fonly if that drug was present at a
OL,18,Fcertain concentration "would it be
OL,19,Fdetected and reported as positive".
OL,26,@pD@EOUrD@HO]rD@NOUuD@IO]wD@XOUxD@YO]zD@
OL,26,AWOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe toxicologist said that
OL,8,F"specifically due to their chemical
OL,9,Fstructure" many synthetic cannabinoids
OL,10,Fsuch as that commonly referred to as
OL,11,F"spice" are unstable and "may not be
OL,12,Fdetected in post-mortem samples".
OL,14,FOverall he concluded that based on the
OL,15,Frange of screening by Ms Quinn and the
OL,16,Fpossibility of drugs breaking down
OL,17,Fprior to analysis, "negative findings
OL,18,Fdo not entirely exclude that Noah had
OL,19,Fbeen administered a psychotropic
OL,20,Fsubstance prior to death".
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@JO]sD@AOUsD@GO]sD@ZOUtD@`O]yD@
OL,26,ATOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FNick Scott, counsel to the coroner,
OL,8,Fasked the experts to elaborate on two
OL,9,Fissues of post-mortem toxicological
OL,10,Fanalysis ` what was the scope of
OL,11,Ftesting (what substances are tested
OL,12,Ffor), and the limits of testing (if
OL,13,Fsubstances can break down to become
OL,14,Fundetectable).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe toxicologists agreed that it is
OL,8,F"not possible" to screen for all types
OL,9,Fof synthetic cannabinoids, as there
OL,10,Fare such a large variety of different
OL,11,Ftypes, and Ms Quinn added that if you
OL,12,Fdon't have access to the specific drug
OL,13,Fto reference it in testing "then
OL,14,Fyou're limited in knowing that your
OL,15,Ftheoretical screening will pick that
OL,16,Fup".
OL,18,FShe added: "Not finding it does not
OL,19,Fmean that it was not there."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@NO]uD@\OUxD@CO]zD@LOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThey further agreed that it "cannot be
OL,8,Fcompletely excluded" that drugs may
OL,9,Fhave been present at the time of death
OL,10,Fthat subsequently were broken down.
OL,12,FDr Elliott said "that does happen and
OL,13,Fis known to happen particularly in
OL,14,Frelation to synthetic cannabinoids,
OL,15,Fthere is a possibility the drug may
OL,16,Fhave been taken prior to death that
OL,17,Fhas become undetectable as a result of
OL,18,Fdegradation".
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@TO]tD@QOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FIn questions asked of Ms Quinn before
OL,8,FWednesday, she listed some of the
OL,9,Fpossible side effects of spice, which
OL,10,Finclude paranoia, psychosis,
OL,11,Fhallucination and depersonalisation,
OL,12,Fas well as physical impacts including
OL,13,Fa lack of balance or co-ordination.
OL,15,FNoah had been captured on CCTV the
OL,16,Fnight he went missing cycling naked,
OL,17,Fand, asked if any of Noah's behaviour
OL,18,Fwas consistent with having taken
OL,19,Fspice, Ms Quinn said it was not her
OL,20,Farea of expertise on which to comment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDr Elliott agreed that some of Noah's
OL,8,Fobserved "unusual behaviour" would be
OL,9,F"best addressed by someone who is
OL,10,Faware of what someone behaving in a
OL,11,Fpsychotic or mind-altering way would
OL,12,Fbe".
OL,14,FDonal Lunny KC, barrister for the
OL,15,FPSNI, presented a police log from
OL,16,FOctober 2021, when Ms Quinn had been
OL,17,Fapproached about the possibility of
OL,18,Fspice being relevant in Noah's case.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@\O]qD@AOUtD@CO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe officer recalled the conversation
OL,8,Fwhere Ms Quinn outlined there were
OL,9,F"countless different variants" of the
OL,10,Ftype of drug making it "near
OL,11,Fimpossible" to look for in toxicology.
OL,13,F"I certainly made them aware of the
OL,14,Flimitations in the testing," she told
OL,15,Fthe inquest.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@^O]rD@XOUsD@KO]uD@AOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FUnder questioning from Brenda Campbell
OL,8,FKC, who is representing Noah's mother,
OL,9,FFiona Donohoe, Dr Elliott said he has
OL,10,Fworked on "hundreds" of cases
OL,11,Finvolving synthetic cannabinoids,
OL,12,Fsince the drugs grew to prominence in
OL,13,Fthe late 2000s.
OL,15,FAsked if he agreed that, "in broad
OL,16,Fterms", Noah's behaviour was
OL,17,Fconsistent with having taken spice, he
OL,18,Fsaid yes.
OL,26,@rD@KOUrD@TO]wD@ZOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe said he had not personally seen the
OL,8,FCCTV footage "but in terms of
OL,9,Fadolescent individual who in the space
OL,10,Fof 20 minutes essentially has no
OL,11,Fclothes, he's falling off his bike" is
OL,12,F"not a common occurrence" and
OL,13,Ftherefore there "does seem to be some
OL,14,Fdisconnect between the normal function
OL,15,Fof an individual".
OL,26,@pD@NOUsD@cO]tD@AOUtD@YO]uD@QOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe added that some stimulant drugs
OL,8,Flike cocaine can cause an increase in
OL,9,Fbody temperature that would lead to
OL,10,Fsomeone removing clothing, but that
OL,11,Fsynthetic cannabinoids do not fall
OL,12,Finto that category.
OL,14,FMs Campbell said that by 6pm on the
OL,15,Fevening of his disappearance, things
OL,16,Fhad started to "go wrong" for Noah,
OL,17,Fand asked Dr Elliott if that short
OL,18,Ftime frame in Noah's change in
OL,19,Fbehaviour impacted his assessment.
OL,26,@xD@POUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773940276
OL,3,CPossible drugs in Noah Donohoe's
OL,4,Csystem can't be ruled out, inquest
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe said that if synthetic cannabinoids
OL,8,Fare smoked "it is rapidly absorbed and
OL,9,Fthe effects are within minutes".
